title: A home with Character - Res Lease in Austin. 2 Beds, 1 Baths
posting_body: ['Check out this charming two-bedroom, one-bathroom home with adorable period details and a large vintage brick facade that is now available to lease in the Central Austin area!', 'Tour the home today and see the adorable interior layout with stunning hardwood floors, and spacious living area that is open to the dining area through an arched entry.', 'The quaint and clean period kitchen comes equipped with a fridge, gas stove, and spacious cabinets.', 'This home is close to UT, bus routes, local restaurants, less than 5 minutes drive from downtown, and with easy access to major highways (35).', '**', 'In person tours required', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Cristian Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 5606527)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
